{"tid":1192843,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"聽日香港警察識做啦","createTime":"2019-06-08T15:36:06.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-09T01:59:17.000Z","uid":48234,"like":31,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"41a8b55572e2f37e638a305ca6bc8d5550af4683","tid":1192843,"uid":48234,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-08T15:36:06.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">你哋大撚把人上過蚑那叫雞<br />\n唔撚好以為連登冇人知<br />\n逃犯條例過咗，你哋都有機會俾蚑那夾上去<br />\n蚑那眼中香港人人都係「犯罪份子」</span></span>"},{"pid":"10fcc4e468e0ae4f895555a54d8e29534cc7f1ff","tid":1192843,"uid":41389,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-08T15:36:26.000Z","msg":"-遊行起點：銅鑼灣維多利亞公園中央草坪 （維園草地）<br />\n-遊行路線：維園草地起點&gt;高士威道&gt; 禮頓道&gt;伊榮街&gt;邊寧頓街&gt;軒尼詩道西行車路&gt;金鐘道&gt;樂禮街&gt;夏愨道&gt;添美道&gt;立法會外行人路終點<br />\n-集合時間：2：30PM<br />\n-起步時間：3：00PM（或維園草地達八成滿）<br />\n-衝定唔衝，自己執生<br />\n-記得宗旨：不散<br />\n<br />\n溫和：<br />\n<strong>【長期置頂】69反送中遊行須知整合</strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1191837/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1191837/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n<strong>[懶人包] 第一次參加遊行的常見疑問Q&amp;A</strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1186623/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1186623/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n<strong>【極重要】69遊行記得帶防Rfid卡套</strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1190797/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1190797/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n勇武： <br />\n<strong>食放題須知，全部資料，一世受用</strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1191403/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1191403/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n<strong>[law撚］被捕人仕須知</strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1189300/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1189300/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n<strong>［抗爭手冊］End game前準備</strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1169374/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1169374/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">黑色三毛警告信號現正生效 6月8日16時</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><span style=\"color: purple;\">表示連登 facebook 網絡廣泛地區已錄得或預料會有每秒三毛回覆量超過70次/禁70次正評的網絡分化攻勢，且攻勢可能持續或於今晚或明朝早上升級。</span></span></strong><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/VNv7C24.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVNv7C24.jpg&h=73f7da13&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\">注意事項</span></strong></span><br />\n<strong>網民應注意username 同 三毛開post 目的 而非三毛post正評數量。<br />\n網民應負皮三毛post 入去屌佢老母 而毋須參與分化討論。<br />\n鍵盤戰士應努力推正經post 例如準備時項去抵擋三毛攻勢。<br />\n三毛會開一啲反共post 減低大家戒心 請細心思考現時網絡上所有言論。<br />\n一般市民應少上連登 關電視 而休養等待明天遊行。<br />\n鬼得一隻 林奠 其他完全唔重要 。</strong><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ZB4gyv7.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZB4gyv7.gif&h=7cacc0df&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"c1e39e8377e2cf83d1af18d2c31dc9ae8eac8502","tid":1192843,"uid":148987,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-08T15:41:17.000Z","msg":"&ldquo;If you want peace, prepare for war.&rdquo;<br />\nFrom John Wick 3: Parabellum"},{"pid":"5b7ee78ce6b153a691c64444c0ae0fa73b09179d","tid":1192843,"uid":130406,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-08T15:43:47.000Z","msg":"[雨傘的教訓] 必須反守為攻 一鼓作氣 佔路無用<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1189418\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1189418</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"f95e40c0ec841bbb0143e55492c9956ba1cf6d02","tid":1192843,"uid":48234,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-09T01:38:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3a1886517fff5f650e4066e08cc47a3f261b1e76","tid":1192843,"uid":143499,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"41a8b55572e2f37e638a305ca6bc8d5550af4683","tid":1192843,"uid":48234,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-08T15:36:06.000Z","msg"